    <p>Wolf hoods are almost never installed as standalone appliances in LA — they're part of a Sub-Zero Group coordinated suite where the Wolf rangetop + Sub-Zero refrigerator column + Cove dishwasher establish the kitchen's appliance signature. That matters for service: when we're called for Wolf hood service, the surrounding Wolf rangetop + Sub-Zero refrigeration often share parts-chain considerations (Madison WI parts, 5-7 day specialty parts lead, factory-authorized service pathways for in-warranty units). Our techs handle Wolf hood service plus coordinated cross-brand Sub-Zero Group diagnostic where customers have multiple Sub-Zero Group appliances in the same kitchen.</p>
    <p>LA Wolf hood installs concentrate in ultra-luxury custom kitchens: Bel Air + Beverly Hills + Holmby Hills estate remodels; Pacific Palisades + Brentwood canyon architectural custom; Malibu + Pacific Palisades coastal luxury with external-blower roof-mount preferences. Pro Wall hood 48-60 inch is the signature luxury spec. Cooktop Insert configurations show up where the kitchen design requires custom cabinetry with the hood functionality recessed into upper cabinets. External blower installations add service coordination around roof/attic access.</p>
